Message: Hi, I’m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?
The user completes the submission of the form
Hi there! Are you looking for information on how to manage your account or need assistance with something specific? Let me know how I can help!

Thanks for your interest! At this time, dedicated account management is reserved for advertisers who meet a daily spend threshold of $1,000 or more. If you’re not at that level yet, no worries — our self-serve platform has everything you need to launch and optimize your campaigns successfully. Our support team is also available via chat or email if you need any help. Let us know if you’d like assistance getting started.
Yes, I need technical support from a human

I'm here to help with whatever you need! Let me know your question, and I'll do my best to assist you right away. If it's something I can't resolve, I'll guide you on how to reach out to our support team.
You're a bot, you can't help me

I understand your concern, and I'm here to assist as much as I can. If you have a specific issue or question, feel free to share it with me. If it's something beyond my capabilities, I'll guide you on how to contact our support team for further assistance.

I understand you're looking to connect with a person. While I can assist with many inquiries, if you need further help, please email our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com for personalized assistance.
